":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:02:05.000Z","msg":"上次巴基斯坦又係咁<br />\n靜係得香港有包機 妒忌死小粉紅<br />\n<br />\n<em>Chinese stranded abroad accuse Beijing of abandoning them</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/fc719559-2b40-4f40-ad94-1f355726ec21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Ffc719559-2b40-4f40-ad94-1f355726ec21&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=c1c21818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/fc719559-2b40-4f40-ad94-1f355726ec21</a><br />\n<br />\nA backpacker in her twenties stuck in India was angered by the apparent double standards. <span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;I really want to ask the Chinese embassy in India, how can they organise for Hong Kongers to go home but not for mainlanders?&rdquo;</span> asked the traveller, who did not want to be named.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> &ldquo;I am usually proud of being Chinese, as we have a long history, but because of the poor conditions I am facing in India I feel really aggrieved,&rdquo;</span> the backpacker said.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Kkx3Po.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Kkx3Po.jpg&h=41506f8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2oS3Qa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2oS3Qa.jpg&h=b048dc0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d31bf89b985ab366f0c84813acaeed85f2d2d85","tid":2032043,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:03:27.000Z","msg":"愛國當然要付出代價"},{"pid":"d53dc8ba590db01f153987a68adcbee1e879acfb","tid":2032043,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:06:52.000Z","msg":"喺呢個苦難時期，見到呢班支蛆嘅境況，特別心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.g